_sText:
Thank you for downloading. Please leave feedback, I gratefully accept any constructive criticism. If you post this to your server please provide the IP, I might just drop in for a bit ;D.

As far as the map itself goes, yes I am planning to make improvements, and add more details, fixes ect. So if you find anything that needs to be fixed please let me know! You can leave a comment about it or just send me a PM (preferably)

Again thank you for the download!
